  "architecture_summary": "Grounding DINO is a dual-encoder-single-decoder open-set object detector that marries DINO with grounded pre-training. It uses an image backbone, a text backbone, a feature enhancer with self-attention and cross-attention, language-guided query selection, and a cross-modality decoder to detect arbitrary objects from category names or referring expressions.",
